script.name: plugin.guilds.comm
script.sourceplaintext:
$page.id = get global variable: name='pageid.guilds'
$guild.data = get global variable: name='guilds.data' $guild = $a.obj -> get local variable: name='guild.owner' $is.hq = $a.obj -> get local variable: name='guild.hq' if $a.obj -> is military outpost @ $military.data = [THIS] -> call script plugin.guilds.utils : type='getMilitaryData' Value1=$a.obj Value 2=null end
do if $guild $agent.page = $guild.data[$guild]['agent.page']
if $a.event == 'commcheck' if $a.data == [Comm.Dlg.ListOnboard] if $guild AND $is.hq if $guild.data if $guild.data[$guild] return [TRUE] end end else if $military.data if $military.data['member'] return [TRUE] end end
else if $a.data == [Comm.Dlg.Captain.Contact] OR $a.data == [Comm.Dlg.Contact] if $a.obj -> is of class Moveable Ship $tracked = $guild.data['tracked.bounty'] if $tracked if size of table $tracked return [TRUE] end end end end return [FALSE]
else if $a.event == 'text' if $guild AND $is.hq $textid = $guild.data[$guild]['agent'] skip if $textid $textid = 111 $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=$textid return $read.text else if $military.data $textid = $military.data['agent'] skip if $textid $textid = 152 $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=$textid return $read.text else if $a.obj -> is of class Moveable Ship $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=1133 return $read.text end
else if $a.event == 'question_face' if $military.data $faceid = $military.data['agent.face'] else if $guild AND $is.hq $faceid = $guild.data[$guild]['agent.face'] end return $faceid
else if $a.event == 'question' if $a.data == 'bounty' $aPassengers = [PLAYERSHIP] -> get passenger array $ret = array alloc: size=0 if $aPassengers $i = size of array $aPassengers while $i dec $i = $p = $aPassengers[$i] $bounty = $p -> get local variable: name='bounty' if $bounty append $p to array $ret end end end if size of array $ret $ret = create new array, arguments=$agent.page, 100004, null, null, null else $ret = create new array, arguments=$agent.page, 100003, null, null, null end return $ret else if $a.data == 'resign' $agent.page = $military.data['agent.page'] $textid = $military.data['agent.resign'] if $textid $ret = create new array, arguments=$agent.page, $textid, null, null, null return $ret end else if $a.data == 'resign.yes' return [TRUE] else if $a.data == 'resign.no' return [TRUE] else if is datatype[ $a.data ] == DATATYPE_SHIP if $a.obj -> is of class Moveable Ship $tracked = $a.data -> get local variable: name='bounty.watch' if $tracked $tracked = $tracked[$a.obj] if $tracked $tracked.time = $tracked[0] $tracked.sector = $tracked[1] if $tracked.time >= 18000 $ret = create new array, arguments=$page.id, 1135, 20000, null, null else if $tracked.time < 600 $id = 1139 else if $tracked.time < 1800 $id = 1140 else if $tracked.time < 3600 $id = 1141 else if $tracked.time < 7200 $id = 1142 else if $tracked.time < 18000 $id = 1143 end $sec.id = $tracked.sector ->get object voice id $ret = create new array, arguments=$page.id, $id, [Page.Sectors], $sec.id, 20000 end else $ret = create new array, arguments=$page.id, 1135, 20000, null, null end else $ret = create new array, arguments=$page.id, 1135, 20000, null, null end return $ret end else if not $a.data if $guild AND $is.hq $agent.page = $guild.data[$guild]['agent.page'] if $agent.page $textid = $guild.data[$guild]['agent.greet'] if $textid $ret = create new array, arguments=$agent.page, $textid, null, null, null return $ret end end $ret = create new array, arguments=$page.id, 1121, null, null, null return $ret else if $military.data $agent.page = $military.data['agent.page'] if $agent.page $textid = $military.data['agent.greet'] if $textid $ret = create new array, arguments=$agent.page, $textid, null, null, null return $ret end end
else if $a.obj -> is of class Moveable Ship $ret = create new array, arguments=$page.id, 1134, null, null, null return $ret end end
else if $a.event == 'answers' if $a.data == 'bounty' $ret = array alloc: size=0 $aPassengers = [PLAYERSHIP] -> get passenger array if $aPassengers $i = size of array $aPassengers while $i dec $i = $p = $aPassengers[$i] $bounty = $p -> get local variable: name='bounty' if $bounty $name = $p -> get local variable: name='bounty.name' skip if $name $name = $p -> get pilot name $price = $bounty['pay'] $price = convert number $price to string $read.text = sprintf: fmt='%s: %s %s', $name, $price, [Text.Credits], null, null $answer = create comm menu answer: id=$p text=$read.text append $answer to array $ret end end end
if not size of array $ret $ret = array alloc: size=1 $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=1126 $answer = create comm menu answer: id='exit' text=$read.text $ret[0] = $answer end return $ret
else if $a.data == 'resign' $ret = array alloc: size=2 $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=1000143 $answer = create comm menu answer: id='resign.yes' text=$read.text $ret[0] = $answer $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=1000144 $answer = create comm menu answer: id='resign.no' text=$read.text $ret[1] = $answer return $ret
else if not $a.data if $guild AND $is.hq $ret = array alloc: size=1 $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=1122 $answer = create comm menu answer: id='view.guild' text=$read.text $ret[0] = $answer if [PLAYERSHIP] -> is docked $guild = $a.obj -> get local variable: name='guild.owner' if $guild == 'bounty' $guild.data = get global variable: name='guilds.data' if $guild.data[$guild]['member'] $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=1123 $answer = create comm menu answer: id='bounty' text=$read.text append $answer to array $ret end end end return $ret else if $military.data $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=1000142 $ret = array alloc: size=1 $answer = create comm menu answer: id='resign' text=$read.text $ret[0] = $answer return $ret
else if $a.obj -> is of class Moveable Ship $tracked.bounty = $guild.data['tracked.bounty'] if $tracked.bounty $key = get next key: table=$tracked.bounty key=null $ret = array alloc: size=0 while $key if $key -> exists if $key -> get local variable: name='bounty' $name = $key -> get pilot name $answer = create comm menu answer: id=$key text=$name append $answer to array $ret end end $key = get next key: table=$tracked.bounty key=$key end return $ret end end end
else if $a.event == 'accepted'
if $a.data == 'view.guild' $guild = $a.obj -> get local variable: name='guild.owner' START $a.obj ->open menu script: script=plugin.guilds.infomenu, value=$guild
else if $a.data == 'resign.yes' $guild = $military.data['nameid'] @ = [THIS] -> call script plugin.guilds.leave : Guild=$guild
else if is datatype[ $a.data ] == DATATYPE_PASSENGER $bounty = $a.data -> get local variable: name='bounty' if $bounty $price = $bounty['pay'] $xp = $bounty['xp'] $name = $a.data -> get local variable: name='bounty.name' skip if $name $name = $a.data -> get pilot name add player money: $price, transaction object=[PLAYERSHIP], page=$page.id, textid=1006, $name, null, null, null, null $read.text = convert number $price to string $read.text = sprintf: fmt='%s %s', $read.text, [Text.Credits], null, null, null $read.text = sprintf: pageid=$page.id textid=1006, $read.text, null, null, null, null display notification: message=$read.text, icon=106 @ = [THIS] -> call script plugin.guilds.doexp : Exp=$xp Guild='bounty' Delay=2000 = $a.data -> destroy passenger end end
end
return null
